Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.57,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kita-san akan menyanyikan lagu ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.06,Main,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lirik ceria.
